# Telecom Churn â€“ Process Mapping

This folder contains the process mapping for the Telecom Customer Churn project, showing both the **AS-IS** and **TO-BE** workflows.

## AS-IS Process
The AS-IS diagram illustrates the current workflow of customer churn management. Key issues include:
- Reactive retention efforts after customers disengage
- Lack of customer segmentation for targeted campaigns
- Insights only available after revenue loss
AS-IS : (https://1drv.ms/i/c/0b3c740fb896ec2c/IQBhzHQxjB3TTKo_FksAdV6dAe09q1nQkAviV_D-Ru6-4Sg?e=sD6nvz)


## TO-BE Process
The TO-BE diagram presents the optimized process addressing AS-IS pain points. Improvements include:
- Proactive monitoring of customer engagement
- Targeted retention campaigns with segmentation
- Follow-up tracking to ensure long-term retention
- Real-time revenue insights to anticipate losses
TO-BE : (https://1drv.ms/i/c/0b3c740fb896ec2c/IQBiyH7-sMlmSaT1InEDK5OhASXDGIkgF0HGWD5lVOph150?e=gAKAVQ)



